Imagine: it’s the end of the world. you and other humans kill all the zombies, the other humans die and it’s only you and your soulmate/BFF/family member alive. they’ve been infected the whole time and your final challenge is to kill them. you kill them and walk across the dry, gray, land. you see green, a color you haven’t seen since the apocalypse happened. you start to get scared, but then, you realize you are going to escape the apocalypse and go into the happy universe. you break through the universe and... wake up. you see a colorful room. it’s your old bedroom. it’s not your old bedroom, you’re in the present. as you go back to sleep, you hear sirens. the apocalypse sirens. your dream predicted the present. now it’s your turn to fight.

I hope this makes sense! 😢😃
